-- Aviva to sell Turkish unit to EMF Capital Partners, unit says
-- 
-- Tue Mar 25, 2014 03:22AM EDT
-- None



ISTANBUL, March 25 (Reuters) - British insurer Aviva <AV.L> agreed to sell its Turkish unit Aviva Sigorta <AVIVA.IS> to venture fund EMF Capital Partners, the Turkish company said on Tuesday.

The statement was made on the Istanbul stock exchange but did not provide details regarding the price of the deal.